definitions.definition: A rubbery polymer formed by cross-linking of polyvinyl alcohol with a boron compound , used as a plaything or to demonstrate physical properties.

main_definition: A rubbery polymer formed by cross-linking of polyvinyl alcohol with a boron compound , used as a plaything or to demonstrate physical properties.

definitions.definition: One who flubs ; a goof , a person who makes errors while speaking.

main_definition: One who flubs ; a goof , a person who makes errors while speaking.
